OL,3,CHugh Grant agrees settlement with
OL,4,Cpublisher of The Sun over hacking claim
OL,6,FThe British actor had reached a deal
OL,7,Fwith News Group Newspapers (NGN), in
OL,8,Frelation to legal action brought
OL,9,Fagainst The Sun, ITV News' Neil
OL,10,FConnery reports from outside the High
