OL,3,CHugh Grant agrees settlement with
OL,4,Cpublisher of The Sun over hacking claim
OL,6,FA judge was told on Wednesday that the
OL,7,FBritish actor had reached a deal with
OL,8,FNews Group Newspapers (NGN), in
OL,9,Frelation to legal action brought
OL,10,Fagainst The Sun.
OL,12,FGrant - who alleged he was targeted by
OL,13,FNGN journalists and private
OL,14,Finvestigators - had previously settled
OL,15,Fa claim with the publisher in 2012,
OL,16,Frelating to the now-defunct News Of
OL,17,FThe World.
OL,19,FNGN has previously denied any unlawful
OL,20,Factivity took place at The Sun.
