OL,3,CHugh Grant agrees settlement with
OL,4,Cpublisher of The Sun over hacking claim
OL,6,FWriting on X, Grant said "I don't want
OL,7,Fto accept this money or settle...Rules
OL,8,Faround civil litigation mean that if I
OL,9,Fproceed to trial and the court awards
OL,10,Fme damages that are even a penny less
OL,11,Fthan the settlement offer, I would
OL,12,Fhave to pay the legal costs of both
OL,13,Fsides."
OL,15,FHe added: "So even if every allegation
OL,16,Fis proven in court, I would still be
OL,17,Fliable for something approaching #10
OL,18,Fmillion in costs. I'm afraid I am
OL,19,Fshying at that fence."
