OL,3,CHugh Grant agrees settlement with
OL,4,Cpublisher of The Sun over hacking claim
OL,6,FGrant said the money from his
OL,7,Fsettlement would be "repurposed" to
OL,8,Fgroups, including Hacked Off - for
OL,9,Fwhich he is a board director of - to
OL,10,F"expose the worst excesses of our
OL,11,Foligarch-owned press".
OL,13,FGrant is among a number of
OL,14,Findividuals, including the Duke of
OL,15,FSussex, bringing claims against NGN.
