OL,3,CHugh Grant agrees settlement with
OL,4,Cpublisher of The Sun over hacking claim
OL,6,FHis claim in relation to The Sun was
OL,7,Fdue to be considered at a trial in
OL,8,FJanuary next year, but a preliminary
OL,9,Fhearing for the litigation against the
OL,10,Fpublisher on Wednesday was told it had
OL,11,Frecently been settled.
OL,13,FAnthony Hudson KC, representing NGN,
OL,14,Ftold a judge that there were
OL,15,F"currently 42 extant claims... that
OL,16,Ffollows the recent settlement of Mr
OL,17,FGrant's claim".
